title: Emilia Clarke Game of Thrones Body Double
text:
We all hear about body doubles, but we so rarely get to see them in their own full light, leading everyone to wonder just how alike these stand-ins could possibly be. In the case of Rosie Mac, the body double for Emilia Clarke's Daenerys on Game of Thrones , the resemblance is remarkable. What's also remarkable is how beautiful she is.
"The best way to predict the future is to create it -"

More From Cosmopolitan According to Yahoo UK , the 18-year-old model, whose pictures have been circulating today, is from Cornwall, England, and lives in Marbella, Spain.
